<HEAD>Question <NOTE PLACE="inter">N&aacute;ttoohtem&acirc;uwetoowunk.</NOTE> How prove you that there is a God? <NOTE PLACE="inter">TOohg&ocirc;dje kor&acirc;men neh &aacute;tta Mandouh</NOTE></HEAD>
<HEAD TYPE="sub">Answer. <NOTE PLACE="inter">Anasquet&acirc;uweten.</NOTE></HEAD>
<P>From the universal and constant agree|ment <NOTE PLACE="inter">Wutche w&eacute;winnakommuk quah yeiache w&eacute;rraw&acirc;|wunk</NOTE> of all Nations, and persons <NOTE PLACE="inter">wutche wame ark&egrave;es, quah skeetamb&acirc;wg mit|t&acirc;uhkuk</NOTE> in the world, who are not void of <NOTE PLACE="inter">terre, oww&agrave;nnak matta s&acirc;uwai<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="1+ letters">&oacute;guk wutche</NOTE> right reason and humanity. <NOTE PLACE="inter">somp&acirc;io penauw&aacute;wuk quah ren&ocirc;owunk.</NOTE></P>
<P>For the things which are grounded <NOTE PLACE="inter">Wutche ai akqusiks chawgwunsh wekakontamoo|awk</NOTE> upon particular mens fancies <NOTE PLACE="inter">skeje nanse&ecirc;awk r&eacute;nwawk r&oacute;ytammo&uacute;ngansh</NOTE> and opinions are not acknow|ledged <NOTE PLACE="inter">quah w&agrave;tramaw&oacute;ytammoungansh matta w&eacute;rramattau|&cacute;omunks</NOTE> of all men, and are <NOTE PLACE="inter">wutche wame r&egrave;nawawk, quah wegonje</NOTE> often changed but this notion that <NOTE PLACE="inter">&agrave;ssowunnaman&ocirc;osh: webe (youhe&ocirc;y<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="1+ letters">&aacute;mmoouk) neh</NOTE> there is a God is common to all men, nor is it chan|ged <NOTE PLACE="inter">Mandoo n&agrave;nnarwee re w&acirc;me r&egrave;nawawk matta &agrave;ssow&uacute;|nu<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="1+ letters"></NOTE> by the changes of times; <NOTE PLACE="inter">&ocirc;oanas spe assowunn&agrave;mo&uacute;ngansh quompaious;</NOTE> therefore it must ar<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="1+ letters">e from <NOTE PLACE="inter">r&egrave;gouche youh paughke m&ocirc;uche song&egrave;me wutche</NOTE> some light, which is common to all <NOTE PLACE="inter">chawgun now&egrave;ta weq<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="1+ letters">-ai, teou nannarwe re wame</NOTE>
<PB N="27" REF="20">
