<PB N="29" REF="21">
and rests upon nothing that was <NOTE PLACE="inter">quah matta chetamssenn&oacute;manah chaugun, n&ocirc;h moh</NOTE> before them all, and made them all, <NOTE PLACE="inter">a kam w&acirc;me nejek, quah kezh&ucirc;w ushan wanne wame,</NOTE> and upon whom all other beings <NOTE PLACE="inter">quah skeje youh wame kat<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="1+ letters">&aacute;ggansh pumm&aacute;yaw&uacute;|gansh</NOTE> depend. And this is <NOTE PLACE="inter">korchet&aacute;msenak. Quah youh atta God Jehovah.</NOTE></P>
