<DIV1 TYPE="question">
<HEAD>But no man can fully know <NOTE PLACE="inter"><HI>Ob:</HI> Webe ma<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="1+ letters">a howan now&ecirc;ta hom tab&acirc;re wauhtawn</NOTE> Gods nature, therefore no God? <NOTE PLACE="inter">Iehovah ri&egrave;wunk [ar&aacute;ndvit] n&egrave;gouche matta Mando?</NOTE></HEAD>
