<DIV1 TYPE="question">
<HEAD>Are there many Gods? or is there but one <NOTE PLACE="inter"><HI>Q.</HI> Sh&acirc;raog Mand&oacute;ak? ux webe &agrave;tta pap&acirc;saguun wah</NOTE> true God? <NOTE PLACE="inter">w&egrave;rramat Iehovah?</NOTE></HEAD>
<P>There are not many Gods, there is only one <NOTE PLACE="inter"><HI>An.</HI> Matta shar&aacute;ou Mandoak, atta webe p&acirc;suk wah</NOTE> true God. <NOTE PLACE="inter">w&eacute;rremat Mando Jehovah.</NOTE></P>
